title: Photo: This Bollywood Actress Was Chilling With Lindsay Lohan In Dubai
text:
Divya Rao Mar . 18 . 2017 
Bollywood actress Anushka Ranjan , who debuted with The Wedding Pullav back in 2015, may not have been seen in another movie after, but she sure manages to get papped where ever she goes. Ranjan was in Dubai recently and turns out, she was chilling with Hollywood starlet Lindsay Lohan . Anushka shared this photo of them on Instagram.
